      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great? I'm parting with my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014carefully maintained and ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value, so if you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that\u2019s been treated right, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
