    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain delivers an unmistakable induction roar as it climbs toward its 8,400 RPM redline, with power sent through a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing Electronic Damper Control (EDC) to manage weight transfer across the subframe effectively. With rod bearings and throttle actuators recently inspected for peace of mind, this chassis offers the mechanical integrity and visceral feedback expected of a high-performance M-division product.",
      "price": 34500.0,
