      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 powerplant, known for its 8,400 RPM redline and eight individual throttle bodies. This example retains its structural integrity with the factory carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof, lowering the center of gravity for improved roll gradient. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock for superior longitudinal and lateral dynamics. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), the suspension offers three distinct damping maps to suit various road textures. The vehicle has undergone preventative maintenance on the throttle actuators and cooling system. While the paint displays minor road-induced patina, the subframe and rod bearings have been inspected to ensure peak operational performance.",
